{
  "stem": "4078.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "You have to find a place to live, a proper place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "She has to have her own room and you have to live a normal life.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "So I remember my mother going to the town hall, and they told her, well, find a place, and then we'll give you coupons for furniture.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And-- and we did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1941 we found a place not too far from where we lived, and so I could go to the same school.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so we lived there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had all this terrible furniture, what they called utility furniture.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But it was new, and I remember the mattress I had was one of those very lumpy things.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You had to sort of shake it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It wasn't-- had no springs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It-- but it was a wartime mattress.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that's where we-- that's where we-- we lived until the-- and-- and I was perfectly content.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It-- I was very happy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I had my own room and I was very happy there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Until the V-1s, the rockets started.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then I suppose I was getting older and I was getting more aware, and it wasn't fun anymore to be in the war.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it certainly-- I knew more about what was going on in Europe and how dreadful [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the Germans were, the Nazis were, and I was just petrified that they would come into England.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the-- they had stopped all church bells in England.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The only time a church bell would ring, they told people, was in case of an invasion.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "If the church bells rang, then you knew that they were sending the parachutists.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The Germans were coming in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I used to have nightmares.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
